snippet.title: Final Fantasy Collection IV V VI | Anniversary Pack (PS1, Jp Ver.) | Cinematic Unboxing
snippet.description:
This commemorative item released only in japan on march 1999. Inside this unique packaging, collectors would find: 3 different games from the franchise (FINAL FANTASY IV, V and VI - all of them PS One versions), an instruction booklet covering all the games and most importantly a table clock with an artwork of Yoshitaka Amano embelleshing its front side. This is the NTSC-J version for the japanese market.
